name: PUNCH Historical Archive 1841-1992 (Gale)
description: Provides the fully text searchable online archive of Punch magazine. The archive a resource for researching and teaching 19th and 20th century political and social history on key themes such as World War I and World War II; Wars and Conflicts; Colonialism, Imperialism and End of Empire; Impact of New Technology and Modernity; Public Health, Conservation and Environmentalism; Social Change; and The Role of Women.
